<P>A COLLECTION OF ESSAYS, ON A VARIETY OF SUBJECTS. IN PROSE AND VERSE.</P>
<P>&mdash;NEWARK&mdash; PRINTED BY JOHN WOODS. 1797.</P>
</DIV1>
