<L>"The Oven!!!" &s;ays Will&mdash;&s;ays the ho&s;t, "why this pa&s;&s;ion?"</L>
<L>"In that excellent bed died three people of fa&s;hion&punc;</L>
<L>"Why &s;o cru&s;ty, good Sir?" "Zounds!"&mdash;cries Will in a taking,</L>
<L>"Who would'nt be cru&s;ty, with half a year's ba|king?</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Will paid for his rooms; cried the ho&s;t, with a &s;neer,</L>
<L>"Well, I &s;ee you've been <HI>going away</HI> half a year,"</L>
