<LG>
<L>Maje&s;tic they ro&s;e in a warlike array,</L>
<L><PB N="5" REF="034482_0081_0FFDE827F7D1B028">And drove from their &s;tations, the tyrants away;</L>
<L>The <HI>heads</HI> of the nation, confounded to &s;ee&mdash;</L>
